    <question><![CDATA[<p><strong>Problem decomposition & subgoals</strong></p>

<p>You break down a large, complex problem into smaller, more easily solvable subproblems or steps. This significantly reduces the scope of the search for a solution. Often, this strategy also involves planning a suitable sequence in which these subgoals must be completed.
<style type="text/css">/* CSS für den Fortschrittsbalken */
    .custom-progress-container {
        width: 350px; /* Breite des Containers */
