    <question><![CDATA[<p><strong>Working backwards</strong></p>

<p>You start with the target state (or a sub-goal) and then look for the operations (operators) that could produce this state from a state closer to the beginning. In other words, you work backwards from the target to the initial state.
<style type="text/css">/* CSS für den Fortschrittsbalken */
