    <id><![CDATA[1226682]]></id>
    <qid><![CDATA[1731398]]></qid>
    <question><![CDATA[<p><strong>Metacognitive and Affective Strategies</strong></p>

<p>These strategies relate to how you manage and persevere with your own problem-solving process. They include self-regulation (e.g., monitoring your progress, assessing the difficulty of the task) and volitional elements (e.g., effort, persistence, belief in your own problem-solving ability).</p>
<style type="text/css">/* CSS für den Fortschrittsbalken */
    .custom-progress-container {
        width: 350px; /* Breite des Containers */
        height: 28px;
        background-color: #e9ecef;
        border: 1px solid #ced4da;
        border-radius: 4px;
        overflow: hidden;
        margin: 15px 0;
        /* Wichtig: Entfernt den Abstand unten, um ihn kompakter zu machen */
        margin-bottom: 0 !important; 
    }
    .custom-progress-bar {
        height: 100%;
        background-color: #28a745; /* Grüne Farbe */
        text-align: right;
        line-height: 28px; 
        color: white;
        font-weight: bold;
        padding-right: 8px;
        transition: width 0.8s ease-in-out;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        text-align: left; 
        padding-left: 8px;
        color: #6c757d; /* Dunkelgraue Farbe für Text bei 0% */
    }
</style>
<div class="custom-progress-container">
<div class="custom-progress-bar" id="myProgressBar"> </div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
    // 1. ExpressionScript-Platzhalter in JavaScript-Variablen laden
    // Stellen Sie sicher, dass diese Fragen Codes existieren!
    const D2 = parseFloat('{D0_D2.NAOK}' || 0);
    const D13 = parseFloat('{D0_D13.NAOK}' || 0);
    const D14 = parseFloat('{D0_D14.NAOK}' || 0);
    const P2 = parseFloat('{P0_P2.NAOK}' || 0);
    const P5 = parseFloat('{P0_P5.NAOK}' || 0);
    const P10 = parseFloat('{P0_P10.NAOK}' || 0);
    const A1 = parseFloat('{A0_A1.NAOK}' || 0);
    const A5 = parseFloat('{A0_A5.NAOK}' || 0);
    const A9 = parseFloat('{A0_A9.NAOK}' || 0);
    const A10 = parseFloat('{A0_A10.NAOK}' || 0);
   const B11 = parseFloat('{B0_B11.NAOK}' || 0);
    
    // 2. Berechnung der Formel: 
    const summe = D2 + D13 + D14 + P2 + P5 + P10 + A1 + A5 + A9 + A10 + B11;
    const formulaResult = (summe - 11) / 44;

    // 3. Umrechnung und Begrenzung des Wertes [0, 100]
    let percentage = Math.max(0, Math.min(1, formulaResult)) * 100;
    const displayPercentage = percentage.toFixed(1); 

    // 4. Visualisierung im HTML-Balken
    const progressBar = document.getElementById('myProgressBar');

    // Balkenbreite setzen
    progressBar.style.width = displayPercentage + '%';
    
    // Prozentwert IM BALKEN anzeigen (immer)
    progressBar.textContent = displayPercentage + '%';
    
    // Wenn der Fortschritt > 0% ist, wird der Text weiß und rechtsbündig
    if (percentage > 0) {
        progressBar.style.textAlign = 'right';
        progressBar.style.paddingRight = '8px';
        progressBar.style.color = 'white';
        progressBar.style.paddingLeft = '0';
    } else {
        // Bei 0%: Text linksbündig und dunkelgrau anzeigen (siehe CSS)
        progressBar.style.textAlign = 'left';
        progressBar.style.paddingLeft = '8px';
        progressBar.style.color = '#6c757d';
        progressBar.style.paddingRight = '0';
    }
</script>]]></question>
    <help/>
    <language><![CDATA[en]]></language>
    <script/>
