   </row>
   <row>
    <id><![CDATA[1226610]]></id>
    <qid><![CDATA[1731423]]></qid>
    <question><![CDATA[While programming, I write temporary notes directly into the code to structure my thoughts before I proceed with the final implementation.]]></question>
