   </row>
   <row>
    <id><![CDATA[1226640]]></id>
    <qid><![CDATA[1731436]]></qid>
    <question><![CDATA[When I am confronted with an error, I first formulate a hypothesis, test it, and then reject or modify it if it fails.]]></question>
